<div id="pf39" class="pf w3 h28" data-page-no="39"><div class="pc pc39 w3 h28"><div class="t m1de x8a h35 y6f7 ff4 fs1e fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LIGHT </div><div class="t m595 x8a h35 y13d ff4 fs1e fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">FOR A </div><div class="t m596 x8a h35 y6f8 ff4 fs1e fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DARK </div><div class="t m358 x8a h35 y4a2 ff4 fs1e fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">WORLD </div><div class="t m54e x3b h36 y6f9 ff6 fs20 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A </div><div class="t m597 x31 h37 y6fa ff6 fs21 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">book about the </div><div class="t m217 xe h37 y6fb ff6 fs21 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath that will radically </div><div class="t m598 x35 h37 y6fc ff6 fs21 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">revolutionize your life! </div><div class="t m512 xc0 h32 y6fd ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">For many Christians, the Sabbath </div><div class="t m537 x64 h32 y6fe ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">doctrine has been taught and practiced </div><div class="t m599 x64 h32 y6ff ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">only in the context of which day is the </div><div class="t m1ab x6 h32 y700 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">right day to worship on. But does the </div><div class="t m313 xa8 h32 y2f8 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath have any relevance to contem-</div><div class="t md9 xa8 h32 y701 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">porary life? </div><div class="t m4bc x6c h32 y702 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Greg Nelson believes the Sabbath is </div><div class="t m56e x3e h32 y703 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">not only relevant but revolutionary. With </div><div class="t m4c1 xa1 h32 y704 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">a passion for turning biblical truths </div><div class="t m197 xa1 h32 y705 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">inside out and revealing the impact those </div><div class="t m52c x55 h32 y706 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">truths can make on our lives, Nelson tack-</div><div class="t m233 x41 h32 y707 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">les questions like: </div><div class="t m59a x41 h32 y708 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">• </div><div class="t m59b x6 h32 y708 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How does our Sabbath keeping impact </div><div class="t m329 xc1 h32 y240 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our family relationships, hurting people, </div><div class="t m4b4 x7c h32 y709 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and the environment? </div><div class="t m59a xaf h32 y8d ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">• </div><div class="t m59c xc2 h32 y8d ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What does the Sabbath say about our responsibility to God&apos;s cre-</div><div class="t m4cd xe h32 y416 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ation? </div><div class="t m59a xaf h32 y107 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">• </div><div class="t m47 x7f h32 y70a ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How does a true understanding of God&apos;s Sabbath impact our </div><div class="t m528 xc3 h32 y70b ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">experience of the Sabbath and how we use it to experience God </div><div class="t m26a xc3 h32 y70c ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">more completely? </div><div class="t m23d x8 h32 y70d ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Through dynamic illustrations and the input from a wide variety </div><div class="t m20b xc3 h32 y70e ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of contemporary authors, A </div><div class="t m59d xc4 hb y70f ff3 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Touch of Heaven </div><div class="t m59e x37 h32 y70f ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">puts forth fresh para-</div><div class="t m59f xc3 h32 y710 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">digms for the day of rest that transform it into a powerful tool for </div><div class="t m349 xc3 h32 y711 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Church and personal renewal. </div><div class="t m5a0 xc3 h32 y712 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Paperback. 0-8163-1721-6 </div><div class="t m123 xc3 h32 y1dd ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">US$12.99, Cdn$19.49 </div><div class="t m5a1 xc3 h38 y713 ff6 fs5 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">From Pacific Press®. </div><div class="t m488 xc3 h38 y714 ff6 fs5 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">We have what you want. </div><div class="t m5a2 xaf h32 y33c ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Available at your local Adventist Book Center, </div><div class="t m5a3 xaf h32 y715 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1-800-765-6955. </div